commentary: Mupariwa to Misbah-ul-Haq, FOUR runs full and wide and that's an excellent shot from Misbah. Drives with a lot of bottom hand to get it into the gap between short cover and mid-off, and the fielder chasing back from mid-off, Chigumbura, trips over as he tries to dive, and ends up sprawled on the ground as the ball rolls away into the boundary. He looks to have injured himself here, and the physio is on the field. His right foot got caught in the turf, and he fell heavily on his left knee. He's back on his feet, and he's being helped off the field. Walking gingerly, but he's walking, and that's good news.
shortText: Mupariwa to Misbah-ul-Haq, FOUR runs
text: full and wide and that's an excellent shot from Misbah. He looks to have injured himself here, and the physio is on the field. His right foot got caught in the turf, and he fell heavily on his left knee. He's back on his feet, and he's being helped off the field. Walking gingerly, but he's walking, and that's good news.
